Completed ARCHITECTURE.md technical design
## Summary
Wrote comprehensive technical architecture covering all components, integration points, and extension mechanisms.

## Changes Made
- Defined 7 core components: SecretsFilteringService, PatternDetector, EntropyAnalyzer, PIIDetector, AllowlistManager, Redactor, AuditLogger
- Documented data models (Detection, Severity, FilteringResult)
- Specified integration points in capture.py (lines 281-300 and 530-532)
- Included ML and contextual analysis extension points for future

